發夢仲要有貢獻
例如義務律師 急救員 召集人 記者
(A) an organizing role;

(B) a first aid responder;

(C) a journalist or member of the media covering or offering public commentary;

(D) a provider of legal services to one or more individuals arrested for participating in such protests; or

(E) a participant who during the period beginning on June 9, 2019, and ending on June 30, 2020, was arrested, charged, detained, or convicted as a result of such participation.
